All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,UserAttribute>
public class UserAttributeMap
extends CaseInsensitiveMap<UserAttribute>

Maintains and ordered map representing the attributes associated with a user's profile.

Map keys are trimmed and converted to lower case. Null or empty map keys are ignored.
